">Love Shayari</a></span><h2 class="posts-hd"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/love-shayari/hakiqat-ho-ya-fareb.html" rel="bookmark">Love Shayari, Hakiqat Ho Ya Fareb</a></h2></header><div class="entry"><p><img class="img-center" src="https://shayarifm.com/image-data/lovely-couple-smiling-love-shayari-hindi.jpg" alt="Hakiqat Ya Fareb Love Shayari in Hindi" width="640" height="640" /></p><p>Tum Hakiqat Ho Ya Fareb Meri Aankhon Ka,<br>Na Dil Se Nikalte Ho Na Zindagi Mein Aate Ho.<br>तुम हकीकत हो या फरेब मेरी आँखों का,<br>न दिल से निकलते हो न जिंदगी में आते हो।</p><p>Nahi Pasand Mohabbat Mein Milawat Mujhko,<br>Agar Wo Mera Hai To Khwab Bhi Bas Mere Dekhe.<br>नहीं पसंद मोहब्बत में मिलावट मुझको,<br>अगर वो मेरा है तो ख्वाब भी बस मेरे देखे।</p><p>Badi Ajeeb Si Bandish Hai Uski Mohabbat Mein,<br>Na Woh Khud Qaid Kar Sake Na Hum Azaad Ho Sake.<br>बड़ी अजीब सी बंदिश है उसकी मोहब्बत में,<br>न वो खुद क़ैद कर सके न हम आज़ाद हो सके।</p><p><a href="https://shayarifm.com/love-shayari/hakiqat-ho-ya-fareb.html" class="rm" >[ Read More Shayari ]</a></p></div></article><div class="ad ad-post"><div class="ad-lebel">Advertisement</div><!-- sfm-res-disp-2 --><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-2320174821842894" data-ad-slot="6548042167" data-ad-format="auto" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins><script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script></div><article id="pid-1099" class="posts"><header class="post-hdr"><span class="tag"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/hindi-shayari/">Hindi Shayari</a></span><h2 class="posts-hd"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/hindi-shayari/fursat-na-mil-saki.html" rel="bookmark">Hindi Shayari, Fursat Na Mil Saki</a></h2></header><div class="entry"><p><img class="img-center" src="https://shayarifm.com/image-data/fursat-na-mil-saki-hindi-shayari.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="Fursat Na Mil Saki Shayari Hindi" width="640" height="640" /></p><p>Daulat Ki Chaah Thi Toh Kamane Nikal Gaye,<br>Daulat Mili To Hath Se Rishte Nikal Gaye,<br>Bachchon Ke Sath Rehne Ki Fursat Na Mil Saki,<br>Fursat Mili To Bachche Hi Ghar Nikal Gaye.<br>दौलत की चाह थी तो कमाने निकल गए,<br>दौलत मिली तो हाथ से रिश्ते निकल गए,<br>बच्चों के साथ रहने की फुर्सत न मिल सकी,<br>फुर्सत मिली तो बच्चे ही घर निकल गए।</p><p><a href="https://shayarifm.com/hindi-shayari/fursat-na-mil-saki.html" class="rm" >[ Read More Shayari ]</a></p></div></article><div class="ad ad-post"><div class="ad-lebel">Advertisement</div><!-- sfm-res-disp-3 --><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-2320174821842894" data-ad-slot="5658771360" data-ad-format="auto" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins><script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script></div><article id="pid-1098" class="posts"><header class="post-hdr"><span class="tag"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/sad-shayari/">Sad Shayari</a></span><h2 class="posts-hd"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/sad-shayari/kismat-se-shiqwa-nahi.html" rel="bookmark">Sad Shayari, Kismat Se Shiqwa To Nahi</a></h2></header><div class="entry"><p>Mujhe Kismat Se Shiqwa To Nahi Lekin Ai Khuda,<br>Wo Zindagi Mein Kyun Aaya Jo Kismat Mein Nahi Tha.<br>मुझे किस्मत से शिकवा तो नहीं लेकिन ऐ खुदा,<br>वो ज़िन्दगी में क्यों आया जो किस्मत में नहीं था।</p><p><img class="img-center" src="https://shayarifm.com/image-data/sad-man-kismat-se-shiqwa-sad-hindi-shayari.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="Kismat Se Shikwa Nahi Sad Shayari in Hindi" width="640" height="640" /></p><p>Mohabbat Haar Ke Jeena Bahut Mushkil Hota Hai,<br>Usey Bas Itna Bata Dena Bharam Toda Nahi Karte.<br>मोहब्बत हार के जीना बहुत मुश्किल होता है,<br>उसे बस इतना बता देना भरम तोड़ा नहीं करते।</p><p>Gujrti BeQarari Mein Na Kam Kar Umar Fir Sari,<br>Ke Hum Bhoole Se Kar Baithe Mohabbat Ek BeDil Se.<br>गुजरती बेक़रारी में न कम कर उम्र फिर सारी,<br>कि हम भूले से कर बैठे मोहब्बत एक बेदिल से।</p><p><a href="https://shayarifm.com/sad-shayari/kismat-se-shiqwa-nahi.html" class="rm" >[ Read More Shayari ]</a></p></div></article><div class="ad ad-post"><div class="ad-lebel">Advertisement</div><!-- sfm-res-disp-4 --><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-2320174821842894" data-ad-slot="3317283360" data-ad-format="auto" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins><script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script></div><article id="pid-1097" class="posts"><header class="post-hdr"><span class="tag"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/friendship-dosti-shayari/">Friendship Shayari</a></span><h2 class="posts-hd"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/friendship-dosti-shayari/dosti-barakaraar-kar-lena.html" rel="bookmark">Shayari Dosti Barakaraar Kar Lena</a></h2></header><div class="entry"><p><img class="img-center" src="https://shayarifm.com/image-data/shayari-for-friend-dosti-barkarar-kar-lena.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="Dosti Barkarar Kar Lena Friendship Shayari" width="640" height="640" /></p><p>Door Ho Jaayein Toh Jara Intezaar Kar Lena,<br>Apne Dil Mein Itna Toh Aitbaar Kar Lena,<br>Laut Ke Aayenge Hum Agar Kahin Chale Bhi Gaye,<br>Aap Bas Humse Dosti Barakaraar Kar Lena.<br>दूर हो जाएँ तो जरा इंतज़ार कर लेना,<br>अपने दिल में इतना तो ऐतबार कर लेना,<br>लौट के आयेंगे हम अगर कहीं चले भी गए,<br>आप बस हमसे दोस्ती बरकरार कर लेना।</p><p><a href="https://shayarifm.com/friendship-dosti-shayari/dosti-barakaraar-kar-lena.html" class="rm" >[ Read More Shayari ]</a></p></div></article><div class="ad ad-post"><div class="ad-lebel">Advertisement</div><!-- sfm-res-disp-5 --><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-2320174821842894" data-ad-slot="6270749766" data-ad-format="auto" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins><script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script></div><article id="pid-1096" class="posts"><header class="post-hdr"><span class="tag"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/romantic-shayari/">Romantic Shayari</a></span><h2 class="posts-hd"><a href="https://shayarifm.com/romantic-shayari/toot-ke-chaaho-mujhe.html" rel="bookmark">Iss Qadar Toot Ke Chaaho Mujhe</a></h2></header><div class="entry"><p>Na Tumhein Hosh Rahe Aur Na Mujhe Hosh Rahe,<br>Iss Qadar Toot Ke Chaaho Mujhe Pagal Kar Do.<br>न तुम्हें होश रहे और न मुझे होश रहे,<br>इस क़दर टूट के चाहो मुझे पागल कर दो।</p><p><img class="img-center" src="https://shayarifm.com/image-data/toot-kar-chaho-shayari-romantic-couple.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="Iss Qadar Toot Ke Chaho Shayari for Romatic Couple" width="640" height="640" /></p><p>Chamka Na Karo Jugnoo Ki Tarha Raat Ko,<br>Le Jaunga Mutthi Mein Kisi Roz Chhupa Kar.<br>चमका न करो जुगनू की तरह रात को,<br>ले जाउंगा मुट्ठी में किसी रोज़ छुपा कर।</p><p><a href="https://shayarifm.com/romantic-shayari/toot-ke-chaaho-mujhe.html" class="rm" >[ Read More Shayari ]</a></p></div></article><div class="pagi-num"><span class="disabled">&lsaquo; Prev</span><span class="current">1</span><a href="https://shayarifm.com/page/2">2</a><a href="https://shayarifm.com/page/3">3</a><a href="https://shayarifm.com/page/4">4</a><span class="gap"></span><a href="https://shayarifm.com/page/10">10</a><a rel="next" href="https://shayarifm.com/page/2" class="next">Next &rsaquo;</a></div></div><aside class="sidebar"><div class="aside-box ab-search"><h3 class="ab-hd">Search Shayari</h3><form action="https://shayarifm.com/" class="searchform" autocomplete="off"><input type="text" class="sbox" name="s" minlength=3 maxlength=50 placeholder="Search this site..." required /><button type="submit" class="ssub">Search</button></form></div><div class="aside-box ab-list"><h3 class="ab-hd">Shayari Categories</h3><ul><li><a href="https://shayarifm.com/shayari-on-eyes/" title="Shayari on Eyes, Aankhein Shayari, Nigah Shayari, Najar Shayari">Aankhein Shayari</a></li><li><a href="https://shayarifm.com/ashq-aansu-shayari/" title="Ashq Shayari, Aansoo Shayari, Hindi Shayari on Tears">Aansoo Shayari</a></li><li><a href="https://shayarifm.com/tanhayi-alone-shayari/" title="Alone Shayari, Tanhai Shayari, Shayari on Loneliness">Alone Shayari</a></li><li><a